<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤٠٠٨ -<span class="c5"> حَدَّثَنَا عَلِيُّ بْنُ عَبْدِ اللَّهِ:</span> حَدَّثَنَا سُفْيَانُ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ إِسْمَاعِيلَ بْنِ أَبِي خَالِدٍ:</span> سَمِعَ ابْنَ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗١٥٥٣⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">أَبِي أَوْفَى يَقُولُ:</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>لَمَّا اعْتَمَرَ رَسُولُ اللَّهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> سَتَرْنَاهُ مِنْ غِلْمَانِ الْمُشْرِكِينَ وَمِنْهُمْ، أَنْ يُؤْذُوا رَسُولَ اللَّهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
